Name: The Walking Dead: Episode 5: No Time Left
Overview: The episodic experts at Telltale Games return, this time putting players in the middle of a zombie apocalypse based on the popular comic and television show The Walking Dead. This series differs from many other episodic games in that players have a limited amount of time to make their decisions, and the choices they make have permanent, lasting effects. The final installment of the season, Episode 5 -- "No Time Left" finds the group's temporary lodging overrun by walkers, while Lee and a small band of survivors head off to find the missing Clementine.
